Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.94,0:00:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, sequestre-me?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.32,0:00:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want the freedom to explore \Nand enjoy all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.78,0:00:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você diz?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.44,0:02:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Onde está o meu Bell?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.31,0:02:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Não vou deixar ele namorar ninguém!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.28,0:02:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hã? Foi eles...?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.15,0:02:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wallen-whatsit! Quit zoning out \Nand help me look for Bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.12,0:02:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu o encontrei.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.87,0:02:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Onde?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.08,0:02:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Talvez.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.04,0:02:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Você fez ou não?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Onde diabos ele estava?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.33,0:02:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lá em cima.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.05,0:02:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Qual é a ideia?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.01,0:02:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.22,0:02:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Não interfira. Dê o fora.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.59,0:02:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Vana Freya?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.80,0:02:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que você está aqui?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.81,0:02:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-Que diabos é isso? O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.94,0:02:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Me dê um relatório de status.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.52,0:02:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim. Eles entraram naquela loja de itens há apenas um momento.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.19,0:02:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Você notou algo preocupante?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.57,0:02:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, shortly before this, \Nthey picked up some luggage at a different shop.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.08,0:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagagem?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Apenas uma mala normal.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.08,0:03:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I could tell, it seemed to be something \Nprepared ahead of time for the date...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Temos alguém na loja?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dois agentes disfarçados estão lá dentro...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.46,0:03:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,, Eles desapareceram!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Syr e Rabbit's Foot desapareceram!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.18,0:03:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.18,0:03:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles usaram algum tipo de item mágico?! Merda!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.22,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Meus pêsames...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.14,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Find them!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles desapareceram?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.77,0:03:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você quer dizer com "desaparecidos"?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.86,0:03:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to ask \Nbefore somebody explains!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,O que diabos está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.45,0:03:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Qualquer sorte?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.37,0:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Apresse-se e os encontre!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tente ali!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.09,0:03:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! So, covering ourselves with this cloak \Nreally does make us invisible, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.72,0:04:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We've slipped through their surveillance net, \Nbut we can't take it easy just yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.85,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Fique perto de mim!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eba! Eu amo isso!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.27,0:04:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Leve-me para um esconderijo secreto, Sr. Bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.27,0:04:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Agora não é hora para brincadeiras, sabe?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu ouvi uma comoção ali!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Encontre-os!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.81,0:04:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Meu Deus, parece mesmo que estou vivendo em um conto de fadas...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos os dias são uma aventura com você.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Não acho que eu me cansaria \Nde estar ao seu lado, Sr. Bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.15,0:05:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem, eu preferiria uma rotina diária \Nque não fosse tão estressante...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.74,0:05:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito por pedir um favor tão incômodo.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.24,0:05:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas eu me sinto como se estivesse no paraíso.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.37,0:05:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é divertido. Muito divertido!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.33,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Agora pode ser bom para nós \Nnos mantermos em baixa até as coisas acalmarem.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Espere, reconheço esse lugar...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, Sra. Syr?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Há um lugar por perto \Nque eu queria visitar juntos.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso estaria bom se eu te levasse lá agora?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim, claro.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.48,0:05:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Onde é esse lugar?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.40,0:05:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Catedral de St. Fulland.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uau!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,É incrível!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.83,0:05:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Normalmente, o público não é permitido entrar,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.83,0:05:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,mas foi aberto aos visitantes especialmente \Npara o Festival da Deusa.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.71,0:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpe pelo desvio. \NEu realmente queria vir aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Não me importo.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.21,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Já me afeiçoei a este lugar, a mim mesmo.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.01,0:06:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Os restos de um Espírito que foi enterrado aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Que tipo de Espírito?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.18,0:06:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Não podemos ter certeza pois o caixão está selado,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.06,0:06:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,mas os arquivos dizem que os restos de uma Undine \Nforam mantidos seguros aqui por milhares de anos.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.57,0:06:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, this entire Cathedral is a historical structure \Nbased on a certain heroic tale.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.49,0:06:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Chama-se "Cais de Água e Luz".
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.95,0:06:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou familiarizado com essa história.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.62,0:06:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about an honorable knight \Nwho teamed up with a sacred Spirit
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Para lutar contra monstros que surgiram do chão,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,e eles se apaixonam um pelo outro no final, certo?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.26,0:06:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem, é assim que vai na versão de contos de fadas,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,mas parece que a história real era diferente.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.84,0:06:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.72,0:06:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Although Sir Fulland exchanged \Na vow of love with the Spirit,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.81,0:06:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,seu coração estava dividido entre ela
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.85,0:06:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and a sister of the sainthood who had intimately \Nsupported him over the years.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.94,0:07:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,E, no final, ele escolheu a santa.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.15,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,É assim?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.78,0:07:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,O Espírito ficou tão abalada por seu amor por ele \Nque tentou matar Sir Fulland.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.66,0:07:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Então... como tudo acabou?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.12,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A Spirit salvou o homem que amava.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Salvou?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles foram atacados pelos monstros novamente,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,e ela se sacrificou para mantê-lo seguro.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.67,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Fulland grieved over \Nthe Spirit's death more than anyone...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.60,0:07:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,e foi construir essa Catedral.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.81,0:07:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,É uma história muito triste.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.60,0:07:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas tenho a sensação de que \Nela contém uma mensagem importante.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.61,0:07:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The hero who failed to keep his loved one safe \Nis telling us not to make the same mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.99,0:07:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,E que nunca devemos desistir.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.45,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, um, I'm not sure what point \NI was trying to make with all this.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Então, hum...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.71,0:07:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.75,0:08:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu entendo perfeitamente o que você está tentando dizer, Sr. Bell.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Suponhamos que eu algum dia fique louco,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,como você lidaria com isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.80,0:08:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Como o Espírito daquela história.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.97,0:08:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ever became so distraught from sorrow \Nor anger that I tried to hurt somebody...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você faria?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu te impediria.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.07,0:08:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,E garantiria que você não pudesse descontar em ninguém.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.99,0:08:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That way you won't suffer \Nfrom the misery of hurting other people.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.04,0:08:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,É só isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Você não vai ficar bravo e me repreender?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum, então...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.54,0:08:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Você não vai me abraçar e sussurrar no meu ouvido:
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mauzinho.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.67,0:08:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou tomar conta de você para que \Nvocê não se meta em mais problemas.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.22,0:08:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare-se.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.89,0:08:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And then drag me back home to stay \Nwith you forever and ever?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutamente não!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.61,0:09:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,E eu estava lhe dando uma resposta séria...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.07,0:09:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Você é mesmo um coração bondoso, Sr. Bell.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu o adoro...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.72,0:09:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Os sinos estão tocando.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.27,0:09:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Srta. Syr, vamos jantar?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.19,0:09:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Já fiz uma reserva para nós.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doesn't seem like any pursuers are nearby.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.45,0:09:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos mexer, Sra. Syr.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.37,0:09:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hã?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho justamente a coisa para você.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.75,0:10:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,An accessory designed after \N"Fulland of Water and Light"!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uau.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.42,0:10:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,These two pieces of silver were made \Nso that if you bring them together...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Veja! Eles cabem perfeitamente!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem, bem!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.72,0:10:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little charm to make sure your romance doesn't \Nend like the tragedy of the knight and the Spirit!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Uau!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.77,0:10:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Staaaare.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Meu Deus, eu realmente gostaria de ter um desses...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.69,0:10:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,querido!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.07,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Desde quando sou "querido"?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.49,0:10:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Aqui está.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.70,0:10:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Obrigado pela gentileza!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Aqui, esta parte é sua.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fica bem em mim, Sr. Bell?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.72,0:10:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.05,0:10:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Está muito bonito.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou guardar para sempre!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.61,0:11:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Diga novamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.86,0:11:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu quero ouvir de novo.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fica bem em você.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.07,0:11:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,De verdade?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim, você é linda.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mais uma vez.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fica muito bem em você.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.91,0:11:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Você é linda.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.54,0:11:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou tão feliz!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare um pouco, Sr. Syr!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.96,0:11:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isso é ruim. Ela totalmente tomou controle da situação.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.38,0:11:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, olhe. Aquilo é nosso destino.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.17,0:11:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Chama-se "Concha Água".
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.14,0:11:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é um daqueles restaurantes flutuantes, certo?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.31,0:11:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,, Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.85,0:11:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Normalmente, fica em uma localização fixa na margem,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.23,0:11:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,mas somente durante esta estação, \Nele vai ao redor de um loop dos canais de Orario.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.78,0:11:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Você... está infeliz com minha escolha?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Não, estou animado!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.82,0:12:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought long and hard about \Nwhere to take me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.79,0:12:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,É surpreendente, já que geralmente o \Ndungeon é tudo em que você pensa!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.75,0:12:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem, dei meu melhor.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.38,0:12:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamospressa e entrar!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.84,0:12:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Atenção hóspedes, o Spoon Aqua agora zarpará.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.26,0:12:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Esperamos que aproveite seu tempo a bordo do navio \Ncom nós enquanto fazemos esta breve viagem.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.56,0:12:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uma vez no mar aberto, nem mesmo \Na Familia Freya deveria conseguir nos alcançar.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.07,0:12:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Então não deveríamos ter problemas durante o jantar.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.57,0:12:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exceto... alguma coisa está errada.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Sr. Bell?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.88,0:12:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.26,0:13:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sinto vários conjuntos de olhos em nós.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.84,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Que bobagem, Bell. Não importa o quão longe você tente fugir,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.18,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,porque Hestia, a Mestra Detetive \N está sempre um passo à frente de você!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.77,0:13:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas não tenho uma boa visão da garota que ele está com ela.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.69,0:13:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Então eu vou me intrometer!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.03,0:13:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Depois que eu terminar de comer, é claro!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.12,0:13:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Miau! Isso parece supimamente delicioso.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.12,0:13:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Não posso só dar uma mordidinha?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Garçons não devem beliscar a comida!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.67,0:13:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Apressem-se e façam o seu trabalho!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.30,0:13:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was the point of us sneaking away \Nfrom the tavern just to wait on tables? Seriously.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.18,0:13:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Não me explique coisas óbvias!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.80,0:13:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the only pawsible way \Nfor us to crash Syr's dinner date!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.77,0:13:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Syr...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.64,0:13:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bell...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.46,0:14:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Você come de uma forma tão graciosa.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,É como se você fosse da realeza ou algo assim.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.67,0:14:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And considering that members \Nof the Freya Familia were guarding you...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.34,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to wonder, \Nare you really just an ordinary waitress?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.60,0:14:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to know who I really am, can you promise me \Nit won't change anything between us?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Probavelmente...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.15,0:14:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu preciso de mais do que apenas um "provavelmente"!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.03,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Não importa quais segredos você tenha,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.03,0:14:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing can erase the relationship we've built \Nand I'll continue spending time with you just the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.46,0:14:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso posso prometer.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.18,0:15:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomar o controle do navio!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.89,0:15:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.06,0:15:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Cara, não é isso um pouco extremo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Espalhem-se e procurem!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.52,0:15:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to reclaim her ladyship from \Nthe clutches of that horny rabbit as quickly as possible!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.78,0:15:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim senhor!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-Que diabos?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.71,0:15:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A Familia de Freya...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Use quaisquer meios necessários!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,E elimine Rabbit's Foot!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eliminar Bell?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Por quê você está atrás dele?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Princesa da Espada?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.39,0:15:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou esperando uma explicação.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.81,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nada disso é da sua conta!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fique fora do nosso caminho!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Se você está aqui para machucá-lo,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.69,0:16:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,então eu terei que impedi-lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.32,0:16:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuide da sua própria vida!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.91,0:16:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, Wallenwhatsit!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.95,0:16:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,O que diabos está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.88,0:16:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tem alguém lutando na sala de jantar.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.88,0:16:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,É a Srta. Ais...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.63,0:16:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sério? O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Encontrei Bell Cranel! Ele está no deque!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeeeek!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos embora daqui, Sr. Bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.31,0:16:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas para onde?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Não há lugar para nós fugirmos!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lá estão eles!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.61,0:16:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu! Todo mundo!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.86,0:16:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpe! Por favor, me ajude!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Você chamou por ajuda?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Maldição, isso significa que ela sabia que estávamos aqui!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.54,0:17:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Não consigo entender nada do que está acontecendo agora, \Nmas qualquer um que tentar atacar Syr...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.46,0:17:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é história!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.80,0:17:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Como isso aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mesmo Ryu e os outros estão aqui?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu realmente não tenho ideia do que está acontecendo!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.72,0:17:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum, Srta. Syr?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.39,0:17:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Você vai pular?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu deixarei você garantir que eu chego seguro, Sr. Bell.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.52,0:17:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.13,0:17:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está bem, Srta. Syr?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum, espero que você não tenha se machucado.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está sentindo dor?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Srta. Syr...?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.64,0:17:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Que viagem!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.56,0:17:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.93,0:18:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,É a primeira vez que faço algo assim!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.49,0:18:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos mexer, Sr. Bell.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.20,0:18:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Espere, Srta. Syr! Você vai se machucar se correr descalça!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Então eu apenas carregarei você se isso acontecer!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.77,0:19:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, oi. Esta é a Ponte dos Heróis.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Faz um tempo desde minha última visita.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been here before, Mr. Bell?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A few times.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.40,0:19:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas o lugar sempre estava muito lotado quando eu vim aqui. \N
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.49,0:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mesmo aqui. Eu nunca vi a Ponte dos Heróis tão tranquila e desprovida de pessoas antes. \N
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,O Grande Herói Albert!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.13,0:19:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele lhe interessa?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.59,0:19:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim, claro.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.84,0:19:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele é o lendário herói que afastou \No Dragão Negro de Orario.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.85,0:20:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, Sr. Bell.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.89,0:20:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Aqui está um fato divertido.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.39,0:20:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why they've never built a statue \Non the pedestal facing across from Sir Albert?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.73,0:20:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Não.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.81,0:20:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it's because there is no one qualified enough \Nto stand face-to-face with the great hero yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.57,0:20:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Qualificado?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.32,0:20:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.24,0:20:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,O mundo anseia por outro herói.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.83,0:20:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday a "final hero" who can defeat the ancient \Ndragon will appear and settle into this empty throne.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.30,0:20:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dizem que é quando a \NPonte dos Heróis finalmente será concluída.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.47,0:20:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Diga-me alguma coisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Você acredita que heróis existem?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.43,0:20:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.72,0:20:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,, Sempre que visito este lugar, \Neu fico tomado por pensamentos incomuns...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.10,0:20:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Minha heroína existe?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.81,0:20:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A hero who will help me with anything \Nand save me from everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.03,0:20:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Um herói só para mim que vai realizar meu desejo.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.16,0:21:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles estão aí fora?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.78,0:21:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu quero conhecer minha Odr.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.41,0:21:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um herói único, só para mim.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Odr"?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.63,0:21:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Minha própria Odr.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sempre sonhei em conhecê-los.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.55,0:21:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Por muito... muito tempo.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.43,0:21:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Encontre Lady Syr!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela deve estar por aqui em algum lugar!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.81,0:21:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nós precisamos correr, Srta. Syr!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.81,0:21:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas droga, para onde vamos?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.73,0:21:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem! Só me deixe cuidar disso, Sr. Bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.53,0:21:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu conheço um bom lugar onde podemos nos esconder!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.90,0:21:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sério? Então mostre o caminho!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.61,0:21:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,O que?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.87,0:21:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? {\alpha&HFF&}Huh...?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.12,0:21:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh...?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.54,0:21:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,WH-WHAAAAAAAAAAAT?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.94,0:23:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Próxima vez: "Seidr".
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.00,0:00:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,opsync,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.93,0:22:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,edsync,
